        <releaseNotes>Support for NetStandard 1.0 https://github.com/damianh/LibLog/milestones/v4.3</releaseNotes>
        <tags>logging, framework, component, nlog, log4net, entlib, serilog, loupe, pcl, netstandars, dotnetcore</tags>
